OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy with some drizzle across
OL,7,Fwestern hills. Elsewhere, it will be a
OL,8,Fdry night with some clear spells,
OL,9,Fespecially in the east. Locally chilly
OL,10,Fin rural spots, with the odd mist or
OL,11,Ffog patch forming. Light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FA cloudy start with some
OL,14,Fdrizzle on western hills. The cloud
OL,15,Fshould break up to give some bright or
OL,16,Fsunny spells into the afternoon. Rain
OL,17,Freaching northern areas late evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
