OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FLargely dry with bright or sunny
OL,7,Fspells Thursday. Feeling cooler.
OL,8,FBecoming unsettled with spells of wet
OL,9,Fand windy weather on Friday and
OL,10,FSaturday. Risk of gales Saturday.
OL,11,FTemperatures near average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
